my wife's phone, isn't it?"],[496,616,"Give it here."],[810,962,"It's my phone, Mr. Duke."],[999,1179,"I just bought a brand new phone case."],[1215,1403,"Maybe it's the one she uses."],[1753,1870,"Okay, whatever."],[1905,1987,"Now just get back"],[1998,2080,"to finding the chairwoman, okay?"],[2088,2204,"If she doesn't turn up soon,"],[2213,2359,"I'm going to have to call the cops."],[2384,2507,"I'm on it, Mr. Duke."],[2554,2758,"The chairwoman's safety is my top priority."],[3020,3121,"Okay."],[5397,5542,"Don't be scared, darling."],[5558,5712,"It'll all be over soon."],[5828,6013,"You're up. Make it quick."],[8032,8175,"Let's break up, Dalton."],[8183,8378,"I'm tired of this life with you."],[8407,8606,"Don't ever speak to me again."]],"23":[[14,168,"Just get me the patient registry now."],[173,248,"Okay?"],[252,379,"Okay, Mr. Dalton."],[1134,1267,"What's going on with Elena?"],[1301,1435,"Why won't she just pick up?"],[1480,1574,"And now she wants to break up"],[1582,1704,"with me out of nowhere?"],[1781,1891,"Something's not right."],[1900,2077,"I heard they're doing a procedure upstairs"],[2086,2203,"on someone's mistress."],[2216,2386,"Some kind of emergency abortion."],[2390,2695,"Really? Oh my God, this is unbelievable, poor woman."],[2703,2812,"Have you heard her name?"],[2821,3015,"I think it's Alana, or something like that."],[3055,3211,"Excuse me, what's the name of the patient?"],[3220,3343,"Mr. Duke, I..."],[3355,3571,"-Tell me! -Elena."],[3580,3741,"-Where is she? -On the third floor."],[3749,3901,"-Take me there now! -All right."],[4784,4884,"How did it go?"],[4930,5030,"It's done."],[5052,5152,"I did it."],[5173,5279,"You sure the baby's gone?"],[5313,5506,"We can't afford to make any mistakes with this."],[5520,5625,"It's gone, ma'am."],[5657,5828,"I terminated the pregnancy."],[6007,6107,"Good."],[6128,6252,"I'll make sure the chairwoman hears"],[6261,6389,"about your loyalty."],[6419,6555,"It's an honor to serve her."],[6621,6735,"Let's go."],[7