a."],[958,1150,"For God's sake, you bitch!"],[1367,1533,"God, what a fucking demon!"],[1751,1895,"Honey, I'm so sorry."],[1974,2211,"Dalton, you're such an actor."],[2220,2545,"You got what you wanted, so drop the act now."],[2584,2693,"No, honey, I wouldn't act."],[2850,3212,"I swear on my mother's life."],[3328,3518,"Honey, look, I love you. I care for you."],[3526,3669,"I would never do this."],[3724,3826,"I would never."],[4243,4444,"I don't believe you."],[4497,4710,"Flora said you never wanted this child."],[4778,4878,"Put me face to face"],[4887,5058,"with Flora, okay?"],[5121,5277,"See how I treat her."],[5286,5424,"I promise you, honey, you won't have"],[5428,5583,"a sliver of doubt in your mind."],[5812,5912,"Fine."],[5930,6179,"Fine. I believe you."],[6985,7088,"But..."],[7230,7524,"Why she did all of this with me?"],[7534,7656,"What's her motive?"],[7665,8017,"Has she ever made a move on you?"],[8026,8130,"Yeah."],[8138,8259,"She hit on me this morning,"],[8292,8449,"but I shut it down straight away."],[8458,8736,"You know, people at the Cooper Company"],[8769,9083,"are under the impression that I'm some aging woman"],[9139,9405,"with no real power or respect."],[9454,9557,"Power."],[9645,9980,"Flora thought I'm your side piece."],[10074,10174,"What?"],[10409,10615,"That's why she attacked me in the meeting room."],[10624,11005,"That's why she went so far to get rid of our child."],[11023,11240,"She wanted me out of the picture."],[11285,11626,"She wanted to replace me and become your mistress."],[11909,12075,"What do you want me to do, honey?"],[12109,12209,"No."],[12234,12350,"Leave it on me."],[12423,12610,"Everything she put me through today,"],[12717,12928,"everything she has taken from us,"],[13009,13113,"I'm going to make her"],[13121,13347,"pay it back a hundred times over."],[13417,13712,"Could you give me your phone, please?"]],"26":[[440,564,"Hello, Mr. Duke?"],[634,846,"This is the chairwoman of Cooper Group."],[872,972,"Are you Flora?"],[1287,1397,"Yes, ma'am."],[1426,1636,"We tried visiting you at the hospital today,"],[1644,1817,"but we couldn't find you in your room."],[1831,1921,"I heard you dealt"],[1936,2124,"with a certain skank on my behalf."],[2132,2238,"Wow."],[2285,2432,"You're very well informed, ma'am."],[2440,2541,"You heard about the news"],[2550,2738,"before I even had time to report it."],[2765,2877,"You did well."],[2894,3132,"I assume the mistress' baby's gone?"],[3213,3313,"Yes, ma'am."],[3345,3543,"And I did it all with you in mind."],[3574,3694,"I appreciate it."],[3733,4073,"Look, let's not let her off so easy."],[4132,4361,"Help me organize some event, Flora."],[4384,4647,"Invite every media outlet in this city."],[4663,4768,"We'll call it"],[4776,5072,"The Public Execution of a Homewrecker."],[5130,5232,"So..."],[5240,5443,"So we're not done torturing her?"],[5469,5648,"The world has to see what happens"],[5657,5793,"to homewrecking whores."],[5809,6088,"And Flora, if the event is a success,"],[6108,6327,"you'll be rewarded with a promotion."],[6395,6638,"Yes, you can count on me, ma'am."],[6697,6934,"I'll make sure everything is done to your liking."],[7002,7318,"But if you don't mind me asking, Mr. Duke..."],[7345,7480,"He made a mistake."],[7531,7707,"I trust it won't happen again."],[7720,7848,"Yes, right."],[7941,8059,"Thank you so much, ma'am."],[8127,8227,"Talk soon."],[8602,8864,"She thinks she's going to be my husband's mistress?"],[8927,9027,"No."],[9076,9162,"She's going to burn"],[9171,9354,"with the whole world watching."]],"27":[[292,467,"Mr. Duke, you asked to see me?"],[543,646,"Yeah."],[692,849,"You've really outdone yourself, Flora."],[857,966,"Uh..."],[1002,1190,"I'm not sure what you're talking about."],[1199,1337,"Everything at the hospital."],[1364,1521,"Do you need me to spell it out to you?"],[1793,1984,"Oh, that."],[2069,2234,"I'm sorry, Mr. Duke."],[2268,2406,"I was, um..."],[2525,2753,"I was just carrying out the chairwoman's orders."],[2844,2972,"The chairwoman again, huh?"],[3001,3101,"Well..."],[3150,3335,"Since we're spelling things out now,"],[3344,3536,"I'm the chairwoman's eyes and ears."],[3604,3694,"She planted me"],[3703,3821,"right beside you from the beginning."],[4341,4441,"But you know what?"],[5247,5347,"Somehow, I think there's more"],[5355,5455,"to it than that."],[5467,5857,"Do you care to reveal your true motivations?"],[5897,6211,"Oh, Mr. Duke, don't get mad."],[6325,6425,"I get it."],[6461,6581,"Every man cheats."],[6649,6811,"It's just a fact of life."],[6853,7080,"But I want to know something about you."],[7514,7646,"What do you think of me?"],[7748,7848,"You?"],[8000,8173,"I mean, a man like you."],[8313,8710,"Rich, handsome, powerful."],[8787,8920,"Who wouldn't want you?"],[8949,9097,"You see, I had to get rid of"],[9106,9267,"that woman for us."],[9377,9523,"She was just standing in the way."],[9559,9714,"And I'm sure you can see it now."],[9747,9949,"Wow, you're definitely the first woman I met"],[9957,10166,"that wanted to be a mistress."],[10422,10534,"That's for sure."],[10543,10815,"Well, it depends on the man."],[10890,11245,"If it's you, I would gladly do it."],[11371,11474,"Hmm."],[11553,11729,"I didn't know you were such a freak."],[11800,11911,"Now you do."],[12090,12303,"You know, I heard the chairwoman is plotting"],[12340,12504,"revenge against my old mistress."],[12722,12881,"You wouldn't have to know what she's"],[12947,13147,"cooking up, would you?"]],"28":[[43,157,"Why are you so curious?"],[259,413,"Are you still hung up on your ex?"],[475,575,"No, not at all."],[589,789,"I just gathered a sharp woman like you"],[811,953,"might be in charge of leading the plan,"],[962,1062,"that's all."],[1339,1582,"Well, if you really want to know,"],[1591,1892,"I've paid top dollar for a sort of"],[1921,2075,"homewrecker shaming crew,"],[2075,2196,"if you will."],[2291,2516,"She is going to get annihilated."],[2739,2850,"That's cute."],[2921,3039,"But you know, as the mastermind"],[3048,3196,"behind all of this,"],[3205,3473,"nobody can find out about us."],[3587,3843,"Because if they do, it will ruin you too."],[3872,4154,"So what? If it means that I get to be with you,"],[4209,4390,"even as your part-time lover,"],[4406,4500,"I'll take whatever"],[4507,4654,"consequences come my way."],[4751,4962,"Okay, I need to get back to work."],[5173,5273,"What?"],[5329,5440,"Get out!"],[7706,7873,"Babe, the livestream is all set up."],[7992,8135,"You look beautiful. You ready to go?"],[8144,8317,"I've still got some words for Flora."],[8355,8495,"So I'll head there first."],[8565,8769,"You show up later with the evidence."],[8787,8887,"Are you sure?"],[8897,9066,"Yeah, I've got this."],[9157,9298,"Today we're showing the world"],[9298,9470,"who Flora really is."],[9540,9832,"And getting justice for our baby."]],"29":[[4083,4225,"Bold of you to show your face."],[4277,4464,"I didn't even have to come get you."],[4762,4889,"Nice venue."],[4954,5114,"You really went all out."],[5245,5356,"Of course."],[5382,5590,"And this is all for you."],[5639,5844,"I even hired the most elite"],[5853,6072,"expose crew ever assembled."],[6107,6415,"You're about to become a national disgrace."],[6522,6785,"The moment you've all been waiting for is finally here."],[6793,6961,"We're livestreaming the Cooper Group's"],[6969,7107,"biggest scandal ever."],[7115,7307,"The public execution of a homewrecker."],[7315,7447,"This is a live broadcast."],[7455,7605,"No script, no filter."],[7618,7796,"And no shortage of the juicy drama"],[7804,7952,"that's sure to unfold."],[7961,8136,"If you're in the area, you should join"],[8144,8314,"this highly anticipated event too."],[8335,8521,"This is as real as it gets, people."],[8529,8641,"It's not staged."],[8663,8775,"You don't want to miss this."],[8906,9006,"Well done."],[9049,9245,"I must say, I'm impressed."],[9396,9516,"Are you crazy?"],[9572,9852,"Can you really not see that this whole thing is"],[9860,10084,"planned out, so we can shame you?"],[10155,10387,"We'll see who ends up being disgraced."],[10424,10524,"Who would it be?"],[10583,10683,"Me?"],[10837,10963,"Guess we'll wait and see."],[11102,11202,"What's wrong?"],[11226,11329,"Are you getting cold feet now"],[11329,11476,"that you've seen the crowd?"],[11519,11599,"Well it's too late"],[11608,11733,"to back out now."],[11833,11982,"Let me give you some advice."],[12030,12152,"Be nice."],[12256,12369,"If you can do that,"],[12393,12593,"I might spare you a little mercy."],[12644,12771,"If you can't,"],[12838,13245,"you'll be neck deep regrets by the end of the night."],[13460,13568,"Please."],[13590,13794,"You really think Dalton is going to come save you?"],[13902,14060,"Well haven't you heard the news?"],[14068,14253,"I'm his new mistress."],[14304,14407,"And you..."],[14422,14596,"You're just yesterday's trash"],[14605,14738,"rotting on the street."],[14834,15046,"All the pain you caused me."],[15088,15274,"All the trauma you put me through."],[15368,15510,"It was just to drive us apart,"],[15519,15771,"so that you could replace me in his bed?"],[15793,15893,"Exactly."],[15929,16107,"Mr. Duke needs a real woman."],[16136,16260,"A woman like me."],[16364,16486,"Let me get this straight."],[16566,16762,"You're a true homewrecker."],[16823,17088,"But you're throwing all this huge party"],[17123,17288,"to expose me?"],[17325,17433,"God."],[17487,17772,"Two-faced, manipulative woman."],[17820,18008,"Like you are really the worst."],[18034,18102,"What?"],[18111,18335,"You can't handle the cold hard truth?"],[18438,18573,"What are you going to do about it?"],[18582,18812,"You wan to slap me if you got the guts for it?"],[18876,18976,"Gladly."],[19058,19166,"Honey?"],[19377,19477,"Come in."]],"30":[[1887,2004,"Honey..."],[2012,2167,"Who's that supposed to be for?"],[2175,2357,"Your non-existent husband?"],[2418,2552,"What, what's going on?"],[2872,3099,"Wait, did you really just call Dalton?"],[3244,3389,"Oh, you thought he was going to be"],[3397,3554,"your knight in shining armor,"],[3560,3660,"didn't you?"],[3848,4021,"Wow, this is priceless."],[4029,4281,"You did something to him, didn't you?"],[4303,4415,"Listen here."],[4455,4746,"Everyone here either works for the chairwoman"],[4754,5115,"or for me, which means that you have no way out,"],[5126,5326,"you stupid homewrecking bitch."],[5439,5539,"Tie her up."],[5697,5821,"We don't expect this."],[6100,6382,"No, please, don't."],[6402,6519,"Don't touch me."],[6538,6722,"No, please."],[7565,7687,"Who the hell are you, huh?"],[7706,7878,"I am the CEO of the Cooper Group,"],[7909,8093,"and I order you to let me go now."],[8125,8270,"I'm sorry, Mr. Duke,"],[8279,8383,"but unfortunately,"],[8391,8603,"we have our own orders to follow at this time."],[8612,8829,"Our plan is to keep you here for three hours"],[8842,8965,"and then let you go."],[8978,9085,"Who put you up to this?"],[9090,9208,"Ms. Flora indeed, sir."],[9224,9418,"Of course it was that bitch!"],[9513,9624,"Oh my God."],[9665,9773,"Elena is in danger."],[9815,9958,"You have to let me go!"],[9967,10093,"I'm sorry, Mr. Duke,"],[10102,10272,"you'll be staying here a while longer."],[10445,10587,"Come on."]],"31":[[121,209,"Let me go."],[218,364,"You won't get away with this."],[565,731,"What are you still mouthing off?"],[759,867,"Gag her."],[1011,1225,"Come here, you stupid bitch."],[1761,1927,"Are we rolling?"],[2139,2452,"Ladies and gentlemen, this right here"],[2752,3022,"is the dirty little slut who's been sleeping"],[3030,3171,"with the Cooper Group CEO."],[3194,3493,"Today, we're broadcasting a live takedown"],[3502,3903,"to show you all what happens to wretched,"],[3950,4150,"shameless homewreckers."],[4200,4374,"So allow me to introduce"],[4439,4634,"our esteemed experts that we've invited"],[4643,4843,"to join us for the proceedings."],[4953,5389,"Our official homewrecker extermination squad."],[7381,7486,"I'm Vlad."],[7494,7676,"I'm the leader of the destruction squad."],[7725,7864,"They call me Greener."],[7917,8033,"And I'm Beatrix."],[8432,8622,"And you're the homewrecking whore."]],"32":[[122,222,"All my friends"],[258,455,"know just how much I absolutely despise"],[464,596,"a lying whore, honestly."],[995,1178,"Let's sort this out, destroyers."],[1746,1838,"Did you really think you"],[1846,2010,"could just get to the top, huh?"],[2723,2823,"So tell me,"],[2857,3043,"are you going to continue prostituting yourself"],[3051,3170,"and wrecking homes?"],[3212,3502,"Please, you've got it all wrong."],[3525,3750,"I'm the chairwoman of the Cooper Company."],[3758,3956,"Flora is the real mistress here."],[4082,4182,"What?"],[4195,4301,"Don't listen to her."],[4320,4540,"She's just saying shit out of desperation."],[4580,4699,"We beat her so much, though."],[4708,4818,"Didn't it do any good?"],[4901,5182,"Hit her. Keep hitting her until she shuts her mouth."],[5391,5634,"Dalton, where the fuck are you?"]],"33":[[939,1145,"Now do you see what I'm capable of?"],[1192,1344,"The harder you beat me now,"],[1352,1552,"the more you'll regret it later."],[1671,1834,"Still with the attitude, huh?"],[1876,2019,"All right, fine."],[2073,2197,"I won't be so harsh."],[2276,2499,"Just admit you're a slimy, dirty whore"],[2507,2688,"and maybe I'll take it easy on you."],[2699,2854,"Give you a little halftime break."],[2867,3063,"Dream on, Flora."],[3111,3219,"Sure."],[3228,3340,"Suit yourself, then."],[3359,3509,"Don't say I didn't give you a chance."],[3596,3764,"What else have you got in your bag of tricks?"],[3808,3928,"So many possibilities."],[3973,4101,"Besides, didn't she just love"],[4110,4310,"seducing men by taking off her clothes?"],[4393,4539,"So let's give her what she loves."],[4591,4741,"-Strip her. -Strip her!"],[4750,4852,"Strip her!"],[4861,4961,"Strip her!"],[5046,5146,"Great idea."],[5188,5290,"Get her clothes off."],[5306,5487,"No, don't!"],[5518,5716,"No, no! Stop!"],[5857,5957,"Stop!"],[6064,6192,"No, stop!"],[6282,6382,"Don't!"],[6989,7089,"Oh..."],[7335,7475,"Oh, look at her."],[7498,7702,"Still trying to hold on to her pride."],[7792,7892,"Too bad."],[7907,8104,"She won't have any left when she's stripped naked"],[8113,8256,"in front of the whole nation."],[8285,8460,"Stop! Stop!"],[8469,8569,"I'm the chairwoman."],[8624,8756,"I'm Dalton's wife."],[8816,8913,"Flora's the one who wants"],[8922,9075,"to be his mistress."],[9126,9226,"Oh, really?"],[9279,9480,"Then who's going to back up your story, sweetie?"],[10212,10312,"I will!"]],"34":[[398,498,"I will!"],[883,989,"Get away from her!"],[1458,1588,"I said leave her alone!"],[1758,1878,"You okay?"],[2501,2816,"I'm so, so sorry, honey. I couldn't get here sooner."],[2907,3016,"You okay?"],[3187,3291,"Yeah."],[3303,3408,"Mr. Duke?"],[3530,3657,"Babe? Hey."],[3829,4027,"I'll take care of it, babe, okay?"],[4120,4228,"They are going to go to hell"],[4236,4436,"for what they have done to you."],[5420,5529,"Mr. Duke!"],[5538,5719,"-What the hell? -What's the matter?"],[5728,5814,"You digging your own grave?"],[5824,5929,"Here, let me help you."],[6044,6158,"No, I was just doing"],[6167,6305,"what the chairwoman told me to."],[6318,6447,"Oh, you were, were you?"],[6474,6606,"Then call her up right now."],[6788,6908,"Mr. Duke, come on."],[6978,7228,"There's no need to lose your cool over this whore."],[7529,7678,"What did you just call her?"],[7934,8100,"You insult Elena again,"],[8114,8314,"and I will cut your tongue out!"],[8582,8803,"Now call the chairwoman."],[8974,9114,"That's an order."],[9212,9467,"Mr. Duke, you cannot be serious."],[9524,9701,"There is no need to lose your control"],[9701,9819,"over that tramp."],[9936,10060,"Have you not understood?"],[10098,10344,"Maybe you're just as stupid as you are toxic."],[10383,10499,"What does that mean?"],[10877,11031,"Everybody here, listen up!"],[11113,11275,"This woman here..."],[11498,11607,"...is my wife."]],"35":[[128,259,"This woman here..."],[479,579,"...is my wife."],[728,907,"And the Cooper Group chairwoman."],[1000,1122,"What did you just say?"],[1173,1296,"You heard him."],[1360,1504,"I'm Dalton's wife,"],[1542,1742,"and I'm the head of the Cooper Group."],[2047,2171,"Wait, what is this?"],[2186,2302,"I don't actually get it,"],[2311,2427,"so where is the real mistress?"],[2438,2775,"Yeah? Someone's been lying to us this whole time?"],[2818,3001,"So, the woman we beat up"],[3010,3265,"in the meeting room is the real chairwoman?"],[3322,3422,"Impossible."],[3475,3650,"Mr. Duke, you're lying to us."],[3667,3804,"And you're trying to trick us all"],[3813,3977,"until the real chairwoman gets here."],[4019,4144,"You're staging this"],[4153,4319,"whole thing to save this skank."],[4355,4493,"Oh my God, you are delusional."],[4546,4646,"You know that?"],[4682,4834,"Someone get Mr. Duke out of here."],[4876,5100,"We're gonna end this bitch once and for all."],[5111,5341,"I don't really know who to believe anymore."],[5396,5523,"Believe me."],[5567,5741,"And if you're going to use that stupid whip,"],[5749,5856,"use it on Flora."],[5867,5969,"She's the one you should have been"],[5977,6109,"punishing a long time ago."],[6154,6254,"Don't forget"],[6269,6560,"that all of your salaries are paid by the chairwoman,"],[6583,6708,"and I speak for her."],[6782,6960,"Which means that until she gets here,"],[6972,7100,"I run this place."],[7165,7387,"Not even Mr. Duke himself can stop me."],[7396,7497,"You're making me laugh."],[7506,7628,"You really just want to get dragged out of here"],[7636,7765,"in handcuffs, huh?"],[8031,8316,"Dalton, why are you protecting this bitch?"],[8414,8689,"You have me now, and it's time to let her go."],[8834,8975,"You make me sick!"],[9205,9381,"Why the sudden change?"],[9389,9539,"You weren't acting like this yesterday."],[9547,9689,"That's because I was testing you."],[9707,9796,"And you know what?"],[9801,9981,"It turns out that you are exactly"],[9987,10139,"who Elena said you are."],[10172,10272,"What?"],[10345,10459,"You tricked me?"],[10536,10706,"All for this gold digger?"],[10768,10868,"I told you."],[10878,11026,"She's my wife."],[11054,11242,"And the chairwoman of the Cooper Group."],[11291,11411,"I made that very clear."],[11488,11588,"You're a liar."],[11638,11740,"You might fool them,"],[11749,11860,"but you're not going to fool me."],[11893,12142,"Guards, apprehend Mr. Duke right now"],[12150,12350,"and this little slut with him too."],[12560,12672,"Security!"],[12680,12880,"If you want to keep your jobs, then move!"],[13431,13659,"The life of the Cooper Group is in the balance, okay?"],[13871,14023,"I am at your service, Ms. Cooper."],[14186,14291,"Ms. Cooper?"],[14299,14399,"Oh no."],[14460,14666,"She really is the chairwoman?"],[14803,14903,"Fuck!"]],"36":[[146,279,"I am at your service, Ms. Cooper."],[288,390,"Ms. Cooper?"],[446,628,"She really is the chairwoman?"],[816,1036,"So you really hired all these people"],[1044,1190,"just to cover up your lie."],[1204,1340,"That couldn't have been cheap."],[1362,1537,"I guess being a gold digging whore"],[1545,1699,"pays more than I thought."],[2099,2203,"Watch your mouth."],[2212,2326,"The person you're talking"],[2335,2535,"to is the head of the Cooper family."],[2696,2958,"So, you really are the chairwoman?"],[3028,3170,"Can you give me your phone, please?"],[5211,5380,"The world has to see what happens"],[5389,5530,"to home-wrecking whores."],[6640,6950,"And Flora, if the event is a success,"],[7026,7229,"you'll be rewarded with a promotion."],[8281,8417,"Ms. Cooper?"],[8498,8758,"I've told you who I was several times,"],[8767,8967,"but not only did you ignore my warnings,"],[9005,9255,"you also proceeded to humiliate and abuse me"],[9263,9401,"on the grounds like that"],[9409,9634,"I was some lowly home-wrecker."],[9680,9884,"Ma'am, I'm so sorry."],[9928,10028,"Please."],[10037,10137,"I didn't mean to."],[10181,10323,"I just wanted to…"],[10340,10589,"To cast me aside and steal my husband?"],[10605,10705,"No."],[10733,10869,"It wasn't like that."],[10882,11155,"A pretty unlucky blunder you made, don't you think?"],[11250,11386,"I'm not the mistress."],[11446,11546,"I'm the wife."],[11645,12011,"The only true chair of Cooper Group."],[12082,12188,"And you, Flora?"],[12343,12461,"You're a liar."],[12557,12662,"A tramp."],[12764,13009,"A lowly, despicable home-wrecker."],[13018,13233,"Please, ma'am."],[13325,13451,"You've got it all twisted."],[13515,13615,"Please."],[13636,13836,"So, let's untwist it then."],[13914,14014,"Honey..."],[14147,14294,"...show them the proof."],[14320,14420,"I'd love to."]],"37":[[164,281,"Every man cheats."],[316,468,"It's just a fact of life."],[501,701,"But I want to know something about you."],[725,831,"What do you think of me?"],[882,1116,"-You? -I mean, a man like you."],[1124,1409,"Rich, handsome, powerful."],[1418,1525,"Who wouldn't want you?"],[1554,1822,"You see, I had to get rid of that woman for us."],[1854,1991,"She was just standing in the way,"],[1999,2139,"and I'm sure you can see it now."],[2157,2357,"Wow, you're definitely the first woman I met"],[2365,2565,"that wanted to be a mistress."],[2831,2931,"That's for sure."],[2943,3194,"Well, it depends on the man."],[3216,3532,"If it's you, I would gladly do it."],[3737,4052,"So, she's the real home-wrecker."],[4064,4185,"And now what are we gonna do?"],[4193,4294,"I have no idea."],[4494,4757,"Let me set the record straight for all of you."],[4785,5068,"Flora tried to seduce my husband,"],[5077,5255,"but he rejected her advances."],[5288,5503,"After that, she convinced herself"],[5511,5672,"that Dalton was having"],[5680,5860,"an affair with another woman."],[5876,6057,"And when she saw me with him,"],[6081,6411,"this idiot assumed that I was the mistress."],[6575,6871,"She thought if she could get rid of me,"],[6942,7142,"she could replace me."],[7347,7483,"And you know what she did?"],[7739,8058,"She murdered my unborn baby."],[8161,8635,"This woman is a savage, heartless monster."],[9422,9582,"Hey, you three!"],[9646,9762,"Stop right there!"],[9782,10040,"I want you to do the job you came here to do."]],"38":[[59,188,"Destroyers, go!"],[638,775,"No! No!"],[791,895,"No, please!"],[905,1037,"No! No!"],[1090,1190,"Stop!"],[2704,2804,"Help."],[4232,4332,"Ma'am."],[4443,4649,"Please. I messed up."],[4718,5038,"Please, just show a little mercy."],[5072,5344,"Oh, so you want mercy now?"],[5376,5616,"Where was your mercy all this time then?"],[5653,5902,"Where was it when you stripped me down"],[5910,6034,"and tortured me?"],[6042,6416,"When I begged you to save my unborn child?"],[6470,6806,"Please, just forgive me just this once."],[6847,6999,"I can make up for it."],[7307,7433,"I forgive you."],[7569,7756,"Oh, please. Thank you, ma'am."],[7764,8032,"-Thank you. -I forgive you,"],[8161,8437,"but my baby never will."]],"39":[[249,394,"If I'd known who you were,"],[477,579,"I would have never done"],[589,766,"this in a million years."],[821,1064,"I know I can't undo anything I did to you,"],[1146,1383,"but just forgive me just this once."],[1482,1830,"It's way, way too late for last chances."],[2010,2110,"But punishment?"],[2290,2442,"There's plenty of time."],[2568,2687,"Ms. Cooper."],[2770,2970,"Forgive me. I was blind, so blind."],[3025,3217,"Ma'am, we really had no idea."],[3362,3482,"I apologize, sir."],[3498,3598,"It was her!"],[3685,3849,"This bitch manipulated us this whole time."],[3858,3995,"She forced us to beat you."],[4021,4192,"We've never seen your face before, ma'am."],[4200,4336,"We were just thinking we were doing"],[4344,4467,"what's best for the company."],[4481,4581,"Amazing."],[4629,4818,"The moment things go sideways,"],[4885,5089,"loyalty disappears."],[5270,5509,"Isn't that right, Flora?"],[5576,5718,"Ma'am, I didn't know."],[5766,5976,"Now you show me where your loyalty lies."],[6040,6150,"Yes, ma'am."]],"40":[[2,217,"Now you show me where your loyalty lies."],[233,333,"Yes, ma'am."],[594,677,"This is what you get"],[677,860,"for surrendering the chairwoman."],[905,1135,"Because you killed her unborn baby."],[1371,1624,"Rot in hell, you disgusting tramp!"],[3932,4219,"No, no, no, no, no!"],[4338,4472,"No, no!"],[4575,4782,"No, no, no, no!"],[5821,5921,"Enough!"],[6218,6632,"So, ma'am, does this mean you forgive us?"],[6675,6919,"Just like with Flora, I forgive you."],[6964,7237,"But my dead baby can't."],[7713,8028,"From now on, you're all fired."],[8084,8173,"The Cooper Group"],[8180,8341,"no more needs your services."],[8350,8468,"And I won't stop there."],[8476,8794,"I'll personally that every single one of you"],[8824,9056,"is bankrupt by nightfall."],[9094,9194,"Oh, no."],[9270,9370,"No."],[10438,10582,"Lock her in a psych ward"],[10590,10858,"in one of those hospitals the Cooper Group funds."],[10939,11092,"And no visitors."],[11172,11272,"Ever."],[11330,11450,"-Yes, ma'am. -What?"],[11502,11602,"Psych ward?"],[11635,11770,"No, no, no, no, no."],[11778,11924,"I'm not crazy."],[11988,12152,"No. Don't lock me in there."],[12238,12338,"Take her away."],[12569,13173,"No, no, no, no, no, no, no!"],[13182,13297,"Please."],[13390,13530,"Stop, please."],[13610,13838,"No, no, no!"],[14019,14179,"I couldn't keep you, my baby."],[14348,14562,"But I brought your killer to justice."],[14788,14909,"I know it's hard, honey."],[15056,15204,"But I love you no matter what."],[15220,15388,"I love you, too."],[16204,16333,"Let me out."],[16429,16575,"Let me out."],[16677,16820,"Let me out."],[17311,17515,"Flora, time for your shots."],[17724,17974,"No, no, no!"]]}